本周的新闻焦点，他发布了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2f808988ff874d2681335e2aee5c6585&amp;amp;_e=bkId9oNtVJZdwbnt8NOjRwxY32wPIhM6Nw_0Hy92SATbCIqsEokdMXII2iMJgVhDgNCtuocsV_FaG-q9zUXVILz_cYr1q9uy7PXSrga_P1dpfA5SD2nuJpyR1Fjd1D9FGtaBRjZzqcGaBXJBVq4-ckhXzGpIRz7uzcfo-hK_oB1n0qrFaetE77hNKZ1Ct4kVbSmjOqxN65Xnk0np7ETXwQLU1KaIAJpm55M5utCulz6T6xj29JMTfkUEmOSISJdCU9eq_5zQ-YfQ2ldMy_sfbrZ-miJbN7YpMDfDBVk-Z0sPTxoMjZKNuwWVOyV4WPPttg2rA4je2zYZhOW1qDU_3w%3D%3D"&gt;一系列行政命令&lt;/a&gt;， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2f808988ff874d2681335e2aee5c6585&amp;amp;_e=bkId9oNtVJZdwbnt8NOjR0Pc1ve3IAi2UP1-RDnqHYKRMO1r_NPZ41_QGtb0lk6IREpjosriOIJFGRkXE803bbY-Ud8Xr7nsMBmPEAnWzzZrJ_TdcVqL-r1RNeF9l0R8grJS12OnEqg00DxQOv3IsYSjnDaY6q5CvLBv2ltjSrBI178YCGAquJdgI_QwWPCeufo_LKeRrBHCvGA544PjXN3piG_6olzXyYDrjUgpwSFfA6DusOb6QzkEfNwPVbX77J4ly23c4N5Rdui3gf9PvK8xTCyLGgKc_gk42xlDRzfsPYduOMVKqiQkMkyEL-JASp_cr0ThxGAD6S-6wbIYYQ%3D%3D"&gt;暗示即将征收关税&lt;/a&gt;，并对&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2f808988ff874d2681335e2aee5c6585&amp;amp;_e=bkId9oNtVJZdwbnt8NOjRyn1ZnSM7kZTo58lNQP6zKilV2-R1jpuWh3by5HCoy6Xo7O1ZSyPCuPw360yfC4QLckNYS00Xke-MOpdOHKLFwTVCQqE0kY0KIQ2GXkvEOE5z_LJEMKp8DUkssPIPyda3uPJmivfaShNaPRkkwe9P-0DK-x1b6cfBAdOudDIymv3Sr0GMMmyaUL8Vpo-CNfEfwmqhwGCMvcY8v-z4o7nfVWD1j-JfZWOsUAIri-2-yevoR1bF6lLhntZcrtpG8FRPfCmnPnIwA62EFsacdZwK-fJf5u49YZnpmhyACgTDU6VV_fC2IynU9kZoIBlDTIPxg%3D%3D"&gt;与生俱来的公民身份&lt;/a&gt;提出挑战。但如果你正在寻找一些反编程的东西，这里有三个有趣的事实可以在晚餐时分享： &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;沃尔格林用智能屏幕替换了一些冰箱门，但在一场价值 2 亿美元的法律纠纷中，制造商切断了数据传输， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=2f808988ff874d2681335e2aee5c6585&amp;amp;_e=bkId9oNtVJZdwbnt8N