XjUpYj9OJUmY4RjAYICX0erOckwTWDDyLojc7VDvXqabhugQ8J7RGqWV1PAqHrryM6mwhBvG8JBnTXt_pSSYvA4YuvEyq-l3Dn8C00pfWtpqUUb8wXi80ddeaTp_ACZmdUxT21jpufVYx1Ypx-AYG3xARywT4yGQ236jepdp7GagKUAgftzWlUMLDVD-XfcdaDwN0ZvXZjmG9w%3D%3D" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1099799&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li=12413954&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=01242025" style="width: 108px !important; display: block;" width="108" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普总统在前往北卡罗来纳州灾区期间表示，他正在考虑&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I2OgxmHM9vJ5ZjQE0s95g5TNn5OYmDEflK-EBQBveEZutPArAKeDuzhHfh69D6RR-_FgJUn_3m-_vJKIo41IcmZJyAq6nAy4OwSrFTTrAhoUDHki63Qp8CqNrmKIj4HjpV76zOr5Om7ukmIB0XmtVd0srgw-KfKE9PcISiFMVWeWbjM1IsjQ3aLFFXMgtkU4CxGvdRxu5uQvvtdjQxqtkyq43mALY2yYmy6ySLeIdiivogIP3QRO5_GLDucd1RWjvy0Jo4wUKhN-yTqXgTi0s75vspKN9FwfOjLTaHy97KSw4StrFSYNvWsRFhYnCClAsw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;废除联邦紧急&lt;/a&gt;响应机构 FEMA。特朗普批评该机构“让国家失望”，并表示该机构未来可能会减少参与恢复工作。在前往加利福尼亚州调查火灾损失之前，他在北卡罗来纳州阿什维尔露面时提出了批评，该市去年遭受了飓风海伦洪水的破坏。自从 10 月袭击北卡罗来纳州的风暴引发一波声称联邦紧急事务管理署拒绝向共和党社区&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7IyKGCvKjvAz_uDx1380XjaDJhGOuMZ9tdE-bmWhXx8b_iko6jFyUrch7dstVsKwUOJEm5v6U9S_gGsh25P5hUQFaewMuRFbStFPTT-2b16-opaSQzYE_FYoFGBmYMrqM7MMCi9iWZhPS7sh82q5pM-qKTUZwD6KwhzKFJza9EqweAR91kYYgpmepgizVbBnmhyOwXpKQPEyCpmlr6_kuwJ24cSirFI2kzRfGBT3bdnogZRW3DLgdY1qHcLTq9k86e2-_lUab9vTKrtQWQLKKkvQSUOohAci3VIJlNkNvdLehNOD0wCJJX2ULfoXw-r0u2w%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;提供援助&lt;/a&gt;的指控（无论是被揭穿还是未经证实）以来，联邦紧急事务管理署一直成为政治焦点。特朗普本人在竞选活动中指责联邦应急管理局&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I8tARcqi4Wizxt9gb-Xv2D41z2H5lCcLqQL_YeLN9Cch15yG6qZLXXYkHSWYDSIBpzqhzHHh5tJEP2j5Hd2yixQ4nkQ_80J3oZYHub2njOR8kNlz15O6imnvrSuITjrpJOSbza2kBFF4DithBzGvozn7kHMaq8kJPTvtD_L5uPUFBmbytiFRmmwQv9Xz07kf2CZNUedX5xhHcjP9K0QsQk_jcdh9uMqCfcSoG2uNrLYtN-1OWzd_-00qNcHOILNTTgphkTZLYhqQksMqwT5VK7ms-ndhjoQSo9oI1_YFmtOvMUktxWhHXHPA6wz-NiRppw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;将资金&lt;/a&gt;用于“非法移民”，拜登政府否认了这一言论。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I2OgxmHM9vJ5ZjQE0s95g5TGJZx04yFNwe-HtbfuSpy89GWUjlSTmZEa2yIg7cmCh_ABXNBuultMndp3Gpl0ctNtH0QR9ZOFqCYsFyHEdBFapHsXnJsylSr8g9e9dRuhbWWa9NTAPctrmJdHxyOGJILuw_U9OUl2hF3omiNfXug0yFjMxMwCTbcfxgpDhXjU7i6jsoGDcUR7fBEy1w6_ynKD6l44oVt_SpYSglPoCaI1GdCxMZ7T65G_idU6KhV5h7kbaHTUmCqtit5EDC9chQ3sCp_FYugeIeya-I3xHVVUrNXWT-gTZ-VRJocZVgEBaQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;本周早些时候&lt;/a&gt;，特朗普提出将救灾援助移交给各个州，而不是让联邦政府做出回应，并任命了一名没有明显救灾经验的前海豹突击队队员作为该机构的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7Ixu4jCXe_ijIlDc3rhzV4u7aNqh4VS6j1Hy4G21KoxJlhp00MvmxkZ30DcSGxYA1x3t1_IYg7PYkJTtiBNK4bBf_LJvXmFXmQE32xklZZFcwQC6NE474X2LHtcrtV5s3m48YU0VMDbPBzI-YRq0SVMpvhd7hADprlNN8NYIH3VFtQ7W-stj7CBcg_SGd853_GuCsdKBjcqvMbPluLm0Wb66_ezmfMV5Il4U3MjXR8C8Vk2APkivvCrUdxNvNso8Nz-srGU9T9aRbEGg7dny1pHoTlqETkiBwePS0cVhJHMvmxANpOxV0DzJsJoMJ9LYp72pQjnmHtDvg9QBDhv_pR4vk4k27LsjjmHsNWz8kirWOizeMxt4M40_HbeIdg1RINSNrKUAX0GrQhy_S-vv-QpyzP1G-Mn1e_D-bPDKUkfXOWS8gKE83dlEn0vIs6f7e4-vX-BBFLmcFowGF70LKktk%3D" target="_blank"&gt;临时负责人&lt;/a&gt;。特朗普没有权力解散联邦应急管理局——只有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7Ixu4jCXe_ijIlDc3rhzV4u4ogYd7A3OdisbJwfBgXsWT1kniXY7ZMkTWvpE3B02cr3-OwU7pdeb_FpitH2dvCJ5QsIduT_H8bD0TQOd8FUT0BVk2Az_18kC8zfo7TcF0ygInna79QwG_3blMw438vqQdNQ_nH23AAOCCGBrGsX-7KJIm6GOQZfnOE759aMsfWbnpuoiC2J-GX55A2Mc_m4Fpv8pY6IAt2hEsNdrtAo3xKNycC40UMIOCXvl5AU4xEKrnshfPJTI7UEtcifokndkUKHekb3D5TMeM3quZpLWOx1yaXKayZCVGUatRkWTCXR1p0SPqaKL2ifOEGnccQeRlwQO8n1TyGAr8L_hARuMZg8qu4qoNPcdPIDmjPA7d_DoSiY4b25GFn-yATcyPo-LNKo4eCddm2J6elbBUG00uc5ZotuM5DkP6CJGtCuJkfQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;国会才有这个权力&lt;/a&gt;。但对该机构的反应进行审查之际，该机构&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I9oPIiS4i4KLnjsrwuXExbJpZTxy99LRQEvZHt8NZhN5cQke42VspZogHwC9ZJn99yq1PbUfBcLemh8OHwqeSBrD7wITfz-eL37MDGdg-T-AySNNJPmpdd1l-QKek2butTd_Wr1cO4oQUvoBwsBb-9G2gD6arH9BWaPBf70_JFvvtGyDDcDGPpJ5bCgp6X85QTNV40xCVZ8sSNGAKgRQTea0VW2dh8W8RN6iSCcvK-n3TKwxnAYaTXOizVO2-qVWDfeLhgt4TZAHqAQqz8YBJ148mJ59sGB68EBD2vJ9nmVfkIZjxiMiiJP_BH82ovj8yA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;仍在积极应对&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I-FPdHbjHJPqAwOiYGXm77gjb3kpZJyPn9VEfTqH6Y5-LiZvsibjbp_mKP8n82xmMtZsS5yOtecwfZw-pC8P_4JXplg84DBY45LWmHouyDuHbAIst-geWKEGKwSLGmrUzWpyogXmABm1UJTeXqQ3QRIxlHIF21oIEVyf0DAYW6NhaINUQscUvkRTpQUDmsbQVoZNxRXDIsZ-IQAIVxyv4oWNIAdMespwq-7lQm1-LT4S7mlbOhZLVXLplLBBZNF-NZ0DWF5M395btAa5ahF8AuAqzHvxVVsdsVU2WhbfJ1bMy7I_e7ut2vks7GWOCGpxnA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;圣地亚哥&lt;/a&gt;和洛杉矶的致命山火，这些山火可能是美国历史上&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I_d0G0NeSu2BYmlb-TUDdsVd1hHt_PDGvAhIRpsfG7-PrCc51wi4OcbEqAhaD4myjXHXTzn4uB7EL-xyxT0IfBrd98G7hgU2nHdDlX7_ALEo01V3W18giOcFImTmzsulyCbtDY4p5Zqgwtzu8yWEfMWKhB-2RtvcuiB8kAPigBPsASHMtSL9FqKs-ewGfB9JFDcRsIe0QyrSr-j3eDXj4Kyug8bwPdIYNICA1u2f4VSj--sX1l3deAPrfUrUHP6auT7q-nio7DgBrAipL3uq7BaXSpxtvBs5SKss6MOWn5hD3DUch0_2Vh0VJD70cnDMYw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;损失最惨重的&lt;/a&gt;山火之一。科学家们长期以来一直警告说，由于人为气候变化，联邦紧急事务管理局本应应对的自然灾害将变得更加危险和更加昂贵，而特朗普已表示他&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I_oHk0WSle-PznHKyJTN75aJ0mGB6JJlApkfPdi-xC2zJGHi2AbMV8naYCX4K6U_Z4F1a11OjXqzUBxKnvSngYYeAwIxXeikkv1jtBNkLm6fw9keDz-hSXmVueUGq66zw9HdzdOtAl8qEIDX4TWRWl48u_RZbeZMmzKcxsljnVWwGNhAwJlaYIh50arPka3Us-ZEiNnLm5iD01_WO8Od1sEEXRNibfOibtyWmtsWIBRjepIdPnZSIIORBab2SDiRjHJcYrOeoSF3nFyBAUiFNWRUcMz8ofYRYMuGD5iDPEPZLc_bAMBvhR_JNX0rzbw9LQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;对解决这一问题不感兴趣&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;span&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7Ix9cxIczFmfkNScHqRlZ9s-2NZO-iCubj2dQsBx7IRm_V-OJYSlcxlZ2j-U4-Rss6LhqDdXEZ6FFb8AH8LUDI_Ry0xrOuW7DW9kM-5GbDXDKU_f4mbXKisLUVYw4ta6m4I3vehRwgJJAEzeUsUdJ3BA9MoGQz1BvwyNERh2z28FLsA55P1_FqxXl7EMhAYT5OGzl47stadaWsyeW1IUjSqbBUkj3FtAvdTEwE4_L6yLLCq-Vmo_9xwLvv9ey6u-ywsxiBSwhE7kszq4Dn_SCsZa_R9fa0jjRg4r_sEnnOQ6Eic3IBrX5F3PrXW3u2G2uGg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em&gt;— 玛格丽特·萨瑟林&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;今天您需要了解什么&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普总统提名的商务部负责人&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;霍华德·卢特尼克&lt;/strong&gt;在一份复杂的道德披露中详细介绍了他在 800 个实体中的财富和影响力。该文件（内阁确认程序的一部分）显示，华尔街投资银行和经纪公司首席执行官&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I7Sqe2l-Hke8CTNXsLf26mFkn3p3GBROxe54XZFj03iEUcHmnYBYE2KN4sEg8-ngB0GdhhzfhOwi0XP1b8e7Vi7YKq96hpOPzxVK08-3iqxBwg7LUWDNeMUgx-Zjo43HAh89OLhzr3U6MdYq0PCqqVcKLRqFY0RuuVtDcaJNprodIL1e12rEtV9e8R0crfMr4K20ds5YSltgljxIqGHhD0v37k4PP30U0LXec3Lmhdci1mrV1_V32hXMYp9wXRj2iNXLju1Cr1xay7cFtNY_yWt8oy9eEbbQg0TR8NuRuXr5dc_RSCMKMOwHgDqUVzrQyQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;坎托·菲茨杰拉德（Cantor Fitzgerald）&lt;/a&gt;拥有价值至少 8.06 亿美元的资产。卢特尼克还确认，他将剥离其在构成其业务集团的三个核心公司中的权益：Cantor Fitzgerald、经纪公司&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I4su_82QZtjlSZ4-Qzetx8u62Vb8PA78ghlXPXxsTAu6OppZLDsgN3mFbZzTKztCXhMNBoOtqI-1iS036hdUnQTrsT7W_8_SQdhtDNv-KrtowGZjf67JRx_KViZgI-8GjgsNnLn8_-RCuza2aYM2CQ1LBzuFp-01GXm-l97XM1SobPknLn-0oRzolORIbw-DE0lU_XfsWH4fc3AFhGysOWoTkd1KB7NY2eEohJlJhvh2PhAq3eppSHCdM9WBaxe3xkqTlrg6IAzVzRjCiJtbklljjzVCxTGhQ7SH4Z9nUj6Lq6FJqRdsDcbKXYJEITd0gg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;BGC Group&lt;/a&gt;和&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I-OeF3cTvYa_SBPKYXVdK2rQRPdYKpZTXeShQ99ZseWb1AeT4PdsIep4jAcKZFlAz3QAWrRga8FXZ0LHdKHl-Y3og7TrTopsi2AzuEmLIkCKky88IqtjefKNp9JJwlzrALa4r5z_Zv-NTN8RMyyeK3HbeYqyzoSLEochN0JHPB0oTKk2NpMfQp2O4tnZExMrz5dDpycdjg6cl6orV1E8AhCZtUgduDwFYn3xERZzxdsKMioOaE-3tl49cJVVjJjI5Jj78fe5jk_XtWY_hgTNdLEy0YGsbjI71_lDtQIQLtyKePpRtnlNfAfuhQcVdKN_rQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;Newmark Group&lt;/a&gt; 。他保留了他的成年子女（其中两名为他的公司工作）可以购买公司股份的可能性。关于谁将接替卢特尼克的房地产公司，人们有很多猜测。与此同时，特朗普四面楚歌的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7IylKNuKDarUFy83fxmYytiL3BmSnqI2JDundcc4RQJQv1hI9PkjRAMUvW4-BIvbp68I3y6CXlSjZJjAXIfc7uQs-xP2mFMsS3MTUI9hdgjhuI5M0aiVLdYmFLULVZHFlvNusDGGgCFkfWC4bKVMJEanjmBE-yhGPJ-5XGiPLrAVfCl5uFIPNhWA7gF1yRwHydNq-q8LZWeypXH-p5vIqplyRhxzHde7agl9HpgfsG88vaZXh4yS0i1U8zCIuQ0iYUspFkgeUQfytAvgvFKzsu2-gHcshRvOahaiKKHOiFT-dv63bjjLg7Mex-8b_a4lZCg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;国防部长&lt;/a&gt;提名人皮特·赫格斯周五晚上面临参议院最终确认投票，特朗普阵营中的一些人想知道为什么乔·拜登总统政府的两名银行业监管机构&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I0o7-S65aM-d97WEBOWwdDnvmWyeBzSDGC5LTakDVyXrDKx66Xt4PLN2YNpBwb7qSjvLFh4ZF30OiBQMySFrdduhlDBVbE78ri-irGPtcIL6FG3akBs_GSnKahelGeIQsF19_9WWuiT09Ytnu-nLE22vR5ZolBAEnrf6yoOa1HaYRUNYU26Vieq4e0pACoN_MkazPUxCORadERqeY3pK-5YlYR8Ap_OpHbUXAlcGAT3XvjHi5fweG0aItB1ZHh8GD_eL4xa-67V_0jig4XFVJV9p4zA0ylK7sbogVaeV-zgBp7YUu_lllz78QS-0SSFjEQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;还没有被解雇&lt;/a&gt;。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;hr style="border-top-width: 1px; border-top-color: #CCC; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-width: 0px; margin: 10px;" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;被驱逐的移民&lt;/strong&gt;被&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I-7oFM2lZ9anWXYx5hu1KIK6LTtP15VZVp-ogVfSMAeG5fp2jlQg5h8FeaJUN_yrCWlNPpz1RhFNE1JvOwAt6Ta3q06BDFM2r6_B18FeYgUpzyT4We-BbFXHPB8lkNpAxKF10v2XVZKvOxeTRRBVQuSHAEYWYOOoswhok5hFgJME_Vz6T_IxWb2r1Whk-Qnf6gtBfSU8W5I8HL-Wj3kNiWbOygEdflzwFkfGmU2Bd_JdCUO9vHhtsJX28nwMvnpMpmI8y9RohHwBCMvhSMWoAICAZkMOUuaCkkvRkHVeZt3WS_1w8GuG-YFEYeOQpnm-YQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;美国军机&lt;/a&gt;送回危地马拉和萨尔瓦多，特朗普团队希望证明他们正在兑现竞选承诺，将数百万移民送回祖国。此次驱逐出境是全国各地围捕移民行动的一部分。在新泽西州， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7Iw_DytF71HVt1JrPrVsCJvOj_u1Y3ujNXxRj6FtG5BCfj75m2MUAux6ayL7VLUUAAGAjuyVW8Vi11ZiRmxTjIUO1x6e2aqp8G_7vSDSdgYf-e0fU14AeCElht65Ncz6gyep2UNSg45z29eM61NwlmAmUhkSbSjP-_1qpdFpubh1JW1NTLG3_ZKBVnQPu-5y0czORscpevAzlwHPitOxT2sAeWH_ZKvrTiEkXHYQKh0UCXWQEGEgeZS71G2Dn7vWuOCncZdzqCN2BouRFy82Q33T8iW1GluRPReoTU8jVsZquRo9D1Vl_GPcxbB6meyALgw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;纽瓦克&lt;/a&gt;市市长和一名民主党国会女议员批评移民和海关执法局涉嫌突击搜查一家企业，在没有出示逮捕令的情况下拘留无证居民。特朗普誓言要针对该国大约 1100 万人没有证件的人，甚至冒着颠覆&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=86ad1633fd254bab932d49382f630600&amp;amp;_e=Ez8Boo9K9OwJrqa2b5W7I44AQXp7Wgrw9G2MrhrjpY-LK8wQI8WCK-WpDmG8HewOk-MVA4xovqXdyqyujy_9BuljDmn-B8ebbs5R36O327CgeOfg9SpYplEN_5-3BUcJ71lstCo7cuKBPnMGOihG94011Hum67el15xBU-7qQ5xmZ-3-dhPdPG-kkKaRtj0g3dKJ1qYSObvofNmdjDTl_YYLCghnu-mBH0Amml-VQhWvg3VwGlMSRvAeVdypEcFVooO1-vgytgPxQ1pvR0stn_HdH7qQ6C8c8v4wFCuN1zhxtaoAjiLWuXrUV3c8xUjfCxGJg-SZAkuNrnc3RX3mTQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;就业市场和美国经济&lt;/a&gt;的风险。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px;" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="ht