"0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;今日达沃斯必读&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;根据 2025 年达沃斯论坛最终结果，全球通胀&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbb7b3064700424aa1a697570d826b2e&amp;amp;_e=6jzeLHQsIPcVRG7tvP9u-O0Gpm4UvyxoE4xK66vgnIs9UTk05tglqzIphp2YLdMcIU91OmdWFKhryBI2K-YXuS8wYpkiwbIBQLnrtxkIYDzsJKieBj3HqmUsPhZZi54FpFCKqporvHVEx8LVoYgn5JUCSgdEAJM4-wT7bvvuaxsifux-zGw6j1meMP6zojjpsFTYEuOuJYJxI1xSPdtkqTQA1kW0Cu7YAfzARquVDOuWvYIFGVBgSyn637imqaA9QW2xpSeevYsjchsfbuSDkdEH_RCl3HhnJz4NMARQscrdkOWwpJAvClojO1DXyzOEKeWWffSg3DcThoxGzFa-vA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;尚未消亡&lt;/a&gt;，中国以外的发达经济体在消费者变化无常和贸易紧张的情况下不能沾沾自喜。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;联合国承认的也门政府副总统表示，特朗普决定再次将也门&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbb7b3064700424aa1a697570d826b2e&amp;amp;_e=6jzeLHQsIPcVRG7tvP9u-CyaR_C5bVX82SaQeh7FcgrXbCvLYpDnHk_u_4-rkyGF-7viP2iW8ToxiCdrRj9WsyJR-WxaqYy1aRsGS1Sg0isoBK4pT_X0iwu6jy2Fn4Orh6CUHEPBj7d3-55hfzhKA5xe0c5-czuEEH6tsMkpZiMbcogYWG_geyJt_lxH7mHlcDkkL8Rz5IzivBXL6pKLvEw78dItiX2ng8r29cSmTvBFMRjNihfrYGoFkjW5z-1VJoM0gArcep8-wEWc3Ug-IlJwiaS_mj5SynBYkpbADGbXKDrmI5kJPBbIE3czlja7V3HLI1XO4YIdJABTEHIczw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;胡塞武装组织列为&lt;/a&gt;恐怖组织，标志着“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbb7b3064700424aa1a697570d826b2e&amp;amp;_e=6jzeLHQsIPcVRG7tvP9u-PGJVnFkwJR-NEjIxx4_QRDZkGufbqh38Q3wCZSq5C31kA7GKeRRxJJQrBtIjLAHFHyUuUb19B4c6QX-W-YgxCicqtn9heeT0IHYTDF3khmfoutdGHEhGkb61nYZDcu7y_3Pve8PnQ86ZroWi_1CKw6KNVZajI26hH5GZ3C_duM9k7RCt7BeNLJSuORiapPOR4jjCEsZJTMgj-r5xbFZE0PP1Yc6K6kPxccdS7mOWBP9x0HpZoNUMzn7lkFLP6onuUzsiNR2_j6iQb5cWajiY7BIpjCRgKzB58cCEfXLCNtxouTbBiPkwOjtlFvI47KAJg%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;他们终结的开始&lt;/a&gt;”。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;经济委员瓦尔迪斯·东布罗夫斯基斯表示，欧盟需要采取更多措施来&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbb7b3064700424aa1a697570d826b2e&amp;amp;_e=6jzeLHQsIPcVRG7tvP9u-LGD1E_DTMJyWnY3R-YQYTW8QaOlS3SG67pqh4bEEs4XGCyQFTRzph-lseeB_ZSYmMSFVcAemP7fBJhipdA2QaRIrg-DpRMR5zdJ33wwiB8353MJtpwbVjfvgquLCpqkbIGcA53b2oS6F_XPv68o4UZ1unwZzTRa9Ehx528Pj0RAFzg7-6Li2vy1MRxDIDPUngD9JdO8lXoWSt1i9dpZ7JkQetLPATxn2hHhelYcercZsv4BDOswOwOnNnAYtIa--CshW79RRQS6b8gUQyGkWFnWIlipGTSoJk2BiYv_gi4Rh1AnZPgsXed4D8hG_I6s8w%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;跟上美国和中国的步伐&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;荷兰银行首席执行官表示，欧盟在开始实施一套全面的资本规则时必须确保不会&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbb7b3064700424aa1a697570d826b2e&amp;amp;_e=6jzeLHQsIPcVRG7tvP9u-EWyre5mqYhcvx8EEGOT9R9PWdkH5yEJGMKZp0ei5233ieZ5b2FozH6Us5tBMFIpF74-BGJPsE750uodszs9FLxD5w_ta5DOBV9tmXI7V2NN_iULELRgdzXkJ5myR22lbb5mmOLDr9cqLs3sqW6Qscrz9nEPjaZmTQygcY010X70vDdG5TX322hH8m5wr6lXIIl28R7KRxDpAduwPJOJnP3_6opCPA3bBE6bP6Ql7SKBt2VAFtirSZbamm3EF-9QXD_WD199O89t0pVUddjPzn5bCx3rxgpONGLeg2a7HXarSs8XHwdqokJxTOCd6QNimQ%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;损害其银行业&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt; EDP​​可能会使用其位于西班牙的燃煤电厂的土地，这些燃煤电厂将被退役用于&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbb7b3064700424aa1a697570d826b2e&amp;amp;_e=6jzeLHQsIPcVRG7tvP9u-CoMcdHxLqToOtDpJSx8xE2DArUc0FA_yB8T4iinUszias2UyUBZWtaQ1AMp9-1QqyOK98qRJn4M-lvhliR2NObKgdYEPhmd6gHHyb7yJGQ5CGeaA9UVK9u_WHGQEaHajtD6OcyRd9iYyAQEV3TFzX6sIOroPPgYFeOXd342jL0TA31M1teyhdEG4bmn8qtjjhw6ZBDaxqNWGZDtOAjrFxMtUcgB1MZ6g6BOhMx46I0TX9W7G4_6jSn1cRrSRkndcF-05dzG0M8N0YjAYnQfPduxx6oPXRbQUlWa7G0e26Xu0qrP-OJrrDhUjfvOQAjA2A%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;数据中心&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;马哈拉施特拉邦首席部长表示，印度金融之都的家乡在达沃斯签署了价值 2000 亿美元的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbb7b3064700424aa1a697570d826b2e&amp;amp;_e=6jzeLHQsIPcVRG7tvP9u-M3VvxQu6fN69Uf7Qa0QO9W2YCkerDxBWml8s3tfeIuS1GZro8OV1ppJB72SdgC5HtlE1OxFAtyGYTGZ8-RcRlsgWFN8z2DrUY5K93O5TvnXTMFAlVHr2daVvK1GONtvd-uA1ddJW-UFggl_dMgRB46RLOi5fpKJcPoJwCaAEmMiQabz1nxTO-DrtnUBnOLHqHWPkCqHjic6K1ucbzKDZVUXBz5Hh_qQR9fnqePBJNwhG9CXt-HMzTDgg7goNZD_IyADur-uWtGc86m-fnP7YcyBPFnTZkbxT2sBEVbyUHIhDqSjWORLWqTwUPMqDFVnuw%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;投资承诺&lt;/a&gt;，其中大部分来自外国投资者。 &lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse;"&gt;&lt;h2&gt;世界经济的其他地方&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;ul style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;日本央行将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbb7b3064700424aa1a697570d826b2e&amp;amp;_e=6jzeLHQsIPcVRG7tvP9u-IPHuzRLYTEmOMg0LotKERuSE2kQekXkc8TkOGUbvtB6Ymuy2G9JLlESPC6_d-_4WROjKSZsB4fhM0vTRoN3VwAy9wVuoxY5WAMMGOI2X8phsuqxEMlalZRytHpeXl0TGGj686SSUIJa4DlWCHuvkRVtfqfQv1jJw05tkTEswAT59jJHjXABUK1ckbAmaS7op3je6O0jaDYXzWwaeyiJHtoBZ1Zf-1kkOHguNG-eCJMDgQHQUXyA2tYw5vpKsBb4X-zoD0SuDihYdJKwFpIlVfD0ceuGqb_VGdgPtRqhfLABI36mHUidl6m7iMkKBtYyTA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;关键政策利率&lt;/a&gt;上调至2008年以来的最高水平，并对通胀强度持更加乐观的看法，引发更多加息预期， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=bbb7b3064700424aa1a697570d826b2e&amp;amp;_e=6jzeLHQsIPcVRG7tvP9u-CU1V3BhvqpZxVm2m18yxcaFWXj-qgVvJwbZdzAxr_lCsV-pgT61Rkt37fKWiiy1HS5FcgiOf8tVBZtEdgLnnIZeSPQ5QmLx4H3Oa7KX_i67yed7UMZfGOCOhB_8LioZgifVWZFtbMX10BudHnqa42ucDyzeL1F9vm8qJ7tZ-dCBFJIBx0fBGaQg38lI9phGWB4gHGvB3vLCvtzKkJzfF3NixhNhQPsxUR0ZJtr4bT_2Nt9plS4MlHFlv9WjEW77s9KvowN9kzHNGfyzG0AhZ2JR7QEe9G49t7Hyp1qWC8v8lweQ8HrLrHJQXlPzQchY0A%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;支撑日元&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, s