llfi1mHpbv3CTQuGba8RvZil7ZCiK4loIQCK06dOU0SwfihUsbDUKrSStVzTtvb7GNKHIk_nsdI6ghRqHoJsveCKKCXUWhI1Hd52plznzOrPN_L_U%3D" target="_blank"&gt;在正确的时间&lt;/a&gt;”与美联储理事杰罗姆·鲍威尔进行交谈，并补充说，他比&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXowFbH1p0sx4uDlQdcrGlWcdAozjvn_sCRbnGk-IyxmQPxGqcsflo5g-TPU9Zf8MUljSkJWkrlGu9CjKJqLPQS2yhorVzI9CLnWtcSpaRSBzWR85bm6zHRK432PWLp9W_vtzqeGQ66d-apfdl2DozMxy4BHXtMrSvaua-y6ZsaqgIvbwkCT4tlaDq2ASgFYCxhoXVIUdhNXM8W4-6R04wH2E%3D" target="_blank"&gt;他在第一个任期内任命的人&lt;/a&gt;“更了解”利率。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;在今天的议程中，&lt;/strong&gt;特朗普将前往北卡罗来纳州阿什维尔，然后&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXo9J1XinQDj4cVf1WTRCvpvJc7GcNFT86xVdJvyAfjvv7q5-NoUIcw0P1NcDyjpwf082ElsaSQsclyDswxYTeJD_yMzL2qUphc2MKB2-V2iafwko5XPYEeO16Gb4Ol9SJSw0OZIK0p6EOZ3lst0unSs2wf0be9llpbKtP7Ty5qAQzbzIXlZ6xHee02WiFFlSRnx4gdMWsfWGkpVIf0FvMPVQ%3D" target="_blank"&gt;前往仍在与山火作斗争的&lt;/a&gt;洛杉矶。加州州长加文·纽瑟姆将采取&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXoz5zALYxPMvp413E_TA5y3SQA2osr3cSGfuQM3Y1mEW9-osyhUpL2AUUcFaTThWVNGqsHWPB5OdcLF287yrZed87X4xMG4E5nV-WKnAWv1PJnnJpC3PD6W2y6UIBPmFtbHS6RREFju-GTyDM8RC_hsvskmEwf484JyBnv1XXhL1vOz6q7IbSMdOqjI1an2tND7pTFvUXfItdZqhUYxVdjvM%3D" target="_blank"&gt;微妙的平衡行动&lt;/a&gt;，因为他需要总统保留数十亿美元的救灾援助，尽管&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXo70Sd6peSwb5bXJRyHNAw1wWtcCQ_ubcdSAr1HluTnFRxk3TWzn-6DrbDgCnRb0sA30nL_HG8MZib3IeIIKxAKPseGqND1csgDYuLl3q5vA1lMmC6_51it0T6mLU3LaCHFkdL_Vj49hjui3kHPMbPM-hqhE0xmMdiuVI7SAVZ3QQefWebe4XTdV2m40zvHUP_R93e1YQcyPlcZrDgfXaCk0%3D" target="_blank"&gt;特朗普的行政命令&lt;/a&gt;明确针对接近该州进步理想的问题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXo4vIyiEzMnGraZBr4PMa1Q1Uo_hrtKVhukSflQdqWB-Guw7seKNKypR6mf6jo6xGMTnp4pMEXW3VonpMQsx_9b_OzgRiJ8tOQr0ugnlq5mf5-A70HvR8vVW7iDngg46ZgKwzJBFgtVT9W-VT3sa4xL1XsAlL90X7ENj3F1JlsXHuQvM3h4oH8u6QTWtdlKKmWtFzlJeM8Uddoj2Z_zaCBeA%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyCuO10W2994/v0/-1x-1.jpg" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iyCuO10W2994/v0/-1x-1.jpg" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 130%; margin-top: 8px;"&gt;杰米·戴蒙.&lt;i&gt;摄影师：Al Drago/彭博社&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;薪酬丰厚：&lt;/strong&gt;摩根大通将首席执行官杰米·戴蒙 (Jamie Dimon) 2024 年的薪酬提高至&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXo4vIyiEzMnGraZBr4PMa1Q3gzLxtXIL2nIIeuaaK5SXLGjZ5yp3U0Ova_hwjx0IcZFlF9qdUmOlrivrVXDmv3cCcG0T21W9WYjdOPwnDdezdqob-wCmpoRZNZImnpue9LrzN5KP3GpJAFN8KAavuduOWhEO-sBnK_IU0jGgGvYMkO_A4obMTijo2adNnl5yQM9g6UB6ZB7vvYMLBvD3cMnY%3D" target="_blank"&gt;3900 万美元&lt;/a&gt;，这一年，这家美国最大的银行打破了自己创下的美国银行业历史上&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXoyArcDDi66UUvc2wug0_Ete2B21faPE2jWqdpi-JLeELx9b4eAxfGPub7AOT3W9oEk7U1JuAzYzjMqwDd94gAkpKdy_QxjA2QtASJggffPNr7S37H_sR3sX9IM9Ho8iOFloC2rHLyqFAcmH_wTjNX0d5xnw8UX3zhxjdJsyktcXGZvvCCjAPSJcV-HBANsGpqKkysqUO24mczA1E0CWhcZk%3D" target="_blank"&gt;年度利润最高&lt;/a&gt;纪录。迪士尼将鲍勃·艾格 (Bob Iger) 的总薪酬提高了 30%，在截至 9 月的一年中为他赚取了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXo1IRBYRY7c9W_RBNzHw0ABCPtNFej8pRWSZFjcneBqs81_dagv6fRYXWffbJ98WInXFRJIG6fcyXuV1atwlgo4XnAzzeg6f5bSvt6bEAVmi0tS8EvnV05O_BIreI_EbW-sQ9lfaSlrV5h59PP5u_va775sYeLqfaSvPlJ6BsCtfywZIKlObiXSJFzo6A46P0P38WQgjBxm2VGOzSn5gRrhg%3D" target="_blank"&gt;4110 万美元&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;审视企业界：波音公司&lt;/strong&gt;又遭受了一个季度的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXoyKlLv7DIMN_TRIZSkwvGYaVx_Lnmg4R4PZkDXORc0e6-gJ0GIo0ifkrpJnh-iwlP7Sf6WE3s8DSX9bjH4ZeLJFHztwEryiuzye47FXHAq_IUhm8MXpvcSO7AZay957mlBiluDFnqdkkVUGiwlb8TYs_dUwwh9K6pr3D9kuRpsvK8G5YKAuWC1XinTtFZ27lXIzYNP9odXpBeOmZEMyXhcU%3D" target="_blank"&gt;新指控和亏损&lt;/a&gt;，凸显了首席执行官凯利·奥特伯格 (Kelly Ortberg) &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXo4vzKBnVTZu3fGconk-Fxcs_NFh2lux9ds6OrjoB2oGmOowPRviK5SUSlUgDEhjexbY1gU-Z_aWo3E7Z-t4xTX_BUESH1tbTf7qyuGtFz-YQQa5oEoTDHv-WAaBJMD2-CmzuLNVsLIQA_ElBhRYOLtHMoZyX0PjWwYR8wJw6U85ih0ha40VC4JAxnd6FNUsiaICuAjuoQwAwa7XcDUqvQKI%3D" target="_blank"&gt;未来的路还很长&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;特斯拉&lt;/strong&gt;还将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXo_yn-Lj4_vGeH1cqOwErst73IC27ArxhU4wOsMuG9zKk-AboNG8WX-UJN93K0e6_4h_r-PHhAsXrUvrOmwHec0zSFD71KeooInGdGib0Agilhr6-fxuuRwPxpCpkRkZAieFmiIsS8u7hBSHprPWgSY5l8qk7o2eFcnCmPW9wAcy2lvjeznfAPkOMtPkJioS3DiQy-NRCN5H1gKi5UDn18Ck%3D" target="_blank"&gt;向中国约 120 万辆汽车&lt;/a&gt;（约占其在中国销售的汽车数量的一半）发布软件更新，以解决车辆动力转向和后视摄像头的问题。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXoyAJeb363FjcYqFMEJ5NuHgAvu3gl-WANiUPspsts77NVgq3YelRsqFBBg39cPr5OcbpNWoFbc9VgcDR0_HInhLQT-UMHq3wddNMZL-rB_9p9QXiSAWygdSNkwZ5KDseQn7_EBMzfCjWSmTZMNaUgkxfFA4G71B8ryMqyPbrbwhoEaNWUZc81LuyC5gg6Q5mvF4fVHjyTrH7VrET_Ht7Sd-fKtHZFAu-V5ST5T6qeQJKEht7oTHec5dSQlYN6nFNd1sjd8RoB5afAWN-n6LJIDF5pG3OGqUpgTe0hCDlu4YbvOvUluiUrKPrfmYDdCjgjA%3D%3D" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" border="0" class="lihide" src="https://sli.bloomberg.com/imp?s=1099764&amp;amp;stpe=default&amp;amp;li_coord=desktop&amp;amp;collapse_width=550&amp;amp;li=12403444&amp;amp;m=d42b0cd27465a66be4227a135cb7a14e&amp;amp;p=01242025" style="display: block; height: auto; width: 100%;" width="550" /&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" colspan="2" valign="top"&gt;&lt;!--[if !mso]&gt;&lt;!--&gt;&lt;div class="lishow" style="display: none; overflow: hidden; width: 0; line-height: 0;"&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" style="padding: 0 0px;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/u/click?_t=f574328d4d0c4c359b90d8e49b10e21d&amp;amp;_m=af807cb073c841dab484db825bddecc6&amp;amp;_e=N9i6kJulGAOonDstTkDXoyAJeb363FjcYqFM